<taxonomicName box="[348,585,1640,1663]" class="Insecta" family="Lophopidae" genus="Binaluana" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="595" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="emarginata">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[348,585,1640,1663]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="595">Binaluana emarginata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
gen. et sp. nov
</emphasis>
., female, SEM images. (42–43) Abdomen: (42) dorso-lateral view, (43) lateral view; (44–45) terminalia: (44) dorso-lateral view, (45) lateral view; (46) anal tube, posterior view; (47) median part of anal tube, dorso-lateral view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1762,2033]" pageId="9" pageNumber="595">
<collectionCode box="[199,265,1763,1787]" pageId="9" pageNumber="595">HEAD</collectionCode>
. Vertex with anterior margin rounded anteriorly. Vertex: proportion A/B = 0.33. Frons: proportion C/E = 0.15; proportion D/E = 0.39.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1762,2033]" pageId="9" pageNumber="595">THORAX. Pronotum: proportion F/B = 0.53. Mesonotum: proportion G/F = 2.12, proportion G/B+F = 0.73, proportion G/H = 0.68. Tegmina: proportion I/J = 3.51.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="598" pageId="9" pageNumber="595" type="description">
