<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,1762,2033]" pageId="9" pageNumber="595">FEMALE TERMINALIA. Seventh abdominal sternite almost rectangular when seen from bellow. The protuberance observed on the middle of the sternite is large and rounded with an important concavity visible above when viewed from behind.</paragraph>
